title: Cal Smart Tzatziki Beef Burgers with Feta and Fresh Salad
description: We all love a good burger. This one – topped with fresh lettuce, tomato and DIY tzatziki – hits all the marks. Served with a bright salad topped with salty feta, this dinner is super satisfying.

